title: Arbor View & Basic features excellent athletes
text: Arbor View & Basic features excellent athletes Will Levi NevadaPrepReport.com In the battle between Basic (3-1) and Arbor View (4-1), the Aggies jumped out to a 21 point lead in the first 13 minutes of the game before holding off the Wolves to take a 21-14 victory. Arbor View has been one of the deepest programs in the state the last six years while the Wolves have surged as annual playoffs contenders.
